Home > Meet the People


Share
Print

		Meet the People
	









 

Innovation. Exploration. Accomplishment. All part of your world of opportunities at Meridian Bioscience 
Become a member of a highly diversified team of enthusiastic people who are committed to innovative achievement in the daily pursuit of improving patient care and saving the lives of millions of people worldwide. 
Our employees will tell you that working at Meridian means thriving in a uniquely creative, forward-thinking, and supportive environment that rewards productivity, accountability, and meticulous attention to detail. Innovation through collaboration is our lifeblood. That’s why they joined our team—and why they stay. We are proud that the average tenure at Meridian is typically more than seven years. It’s a legacy of maintaining the experience and knowledge of some of the smartest minds from around the world. 
"I respect what we do—helping people—and everyone here seems to work a little bit harder because of what we do." — Keri McNamee
They’ll also tell you that we focus on success by empowering our employees to create novel, dependable solutions that both help our valued customers and improve our products and processes. And not just in the lab: No matter what department you investigate, you’ll find a great opportunity for innovation and satisfaction. In fact, we even encourage collaborative creativity within our social activities: An employee committee conceives and delivers fun, engaging events like our holiday party, summer family picnic, and employee appreciation day.
"No matter how busy or big Meridian gets, management is committed to pulling everyone together—right down to the odd and funny games that break the ice at social events. Even Jack [CEO John A. Kraeutler] plays." — Jason Bowman
Bring your track record of success to Meridian and thrive
Learn more about Life at Meridian



