Home > C. difficile


Share
Print

        Products: C. difficile







illumigene® Molecular Diagnostic
                                System




Premier®





                            The illumigene® Molecular Diagnostic
                            System is simple, delivering the power of molecular technology in a "rapid test"
                            type format; flexible, integrating easily into any facility regardless of volume
                            or expertise; and cost-effective, allowing addition of molecular assays without
                            the cost of additional labor or capital expenditures.
                        




                            Leading microwell enzyme immunoassay for the detection of toxins A&B in stool
                            from the C. difficile testing experts at Meridian Bioscience®.
                            Reliable, reproducible results with 95% sensitivity and 97% specificity. Rapid results
                            with procedural flexibility (20 or 50 minute incubation).
                        





illumigene® C. difficile






Premier® Toxins A&B
Premier® C. difficile
                                    GDH











ImmunoCard®




                             
                        




Leading rapid enzyme immunoassay
                                for the detection of toxins A&B in stool from Meridian Bioscience®,
                                the C. difficile testing expert. 95% sensitivity in detection of C. difficile
                                infection; 99% NPV to rapidly rule out negatives. Fifteen minute turnaround time
                                to expedite appropriate treatment decisions.




                             
                        




ImmunoCard®
                                    Toxins A&B
ImmunoCard®
C. difficile GDH





                             
                        




















